Zhang Guangjun was appointed Vice Governor of Guangdong Province .
The fifth meeting of the Standing Committee of the Thirteen People &apos;s Congress of Guangdong Province held its second plenary meeting in Guangzhou on the 30th .
The meeting decided , by a vote , to appoint Zhang Guangjun as Vice @-@ Governor of the Guangdong Provincial People &apos;s Government .
Previously , Zhang Guangjun served as Deputy Secretary of the Party Committee of the China Engineering and Physics Institute .
Curricula vitae of Comrade Zhang Guangjun : Zhang Guangjun , male , Han ethnic group , born in February 1968 , Chongqing , joined the Party in April 1994 , participated in work in July 1991 , graduated from the Faculty of Radio Engineering of Harbin Industrial University in the field of electronics and surveying technology , college degrees , senior engineers , experts in special government allowances under the State Council .
He is currently Vice Governor and Member of the Party Group of Guangdong Provincial Government .
1987 @-@ 1991 Specialization in Electronics and Surveying Technology , Department of Radio Engineering , Harbin Industrial University
1991 @-@ 1998 Technician , Deputy Director , Party Branch Secretary and Deputy Director , General Engineering Institute , China Engineering and Physics Institute
1998 @-@ 2002 Deputy Director and Deputy Secretary of the Party Committee , General Engineering Research Institute , China Institute of Engineering and Physics ( during which : 1999.05 @-@ 2000.12 also served as Secretary of the Institute &apos;s Discipline Inspection Committee , 2001.09 @-@ 2001.12 cadres at the local department level , Party School , Sichuan Province Committee )
2002 @-@ 2002 Party Secretary and Deputy Director , General Engineering Institute , China Institute of Engineering and Physics ( during which : 2002.03 @-@ 2004.05 Postgraduate studies in management sciences and engineering , Fudan University School of Management )
2002 @-@ 2009 Director of Political Affairs , Director of the Office of the Party Committee , Vice @-@ President of the Party School , China Engineering and Physics Institute ( between : 2005.09 and 2006.01 )
2009 @-@ 2014 Director , Office of Major Special Management , China Institute of Engineering and Physics ( between : 2011.09 and 2012.01 )
