In recent years , chickens have continued to upgrade five major functions of industrial clusters , logistics hubs , integrated services , open highlands , and human cohesion around the goal of building internationalized cities along the &quot; one belt , one road &quot; initiative , equipping manufacturing cities , historic and cultural cities , and beautiful and happy cities for liveable industries to accelerate catch @-@ up and high @-@ quality development .
In 2017 , regional GDP reached 218 billion yuan , an increase of 8.7 per cent .
He has won more than 20 national honours , including the National Wenming City , the National Ecological Park City and the China Habitat Environment Award .
Yan Nemin , a member of the Standing Committee of Urumqi Municipal Committee and deputy mayor , introduced that Urumqi , as a major town on the Silk Road with a new northern route , has a special geographical location advantage . From ancient times , it has been connecting the north and south of Tianshan Shandong , communicating between Xinjiang and the mainland , and connecting China to Central Asia , West Asia and Europe in important corridors . It is an important window for China to open up to the west and exchange economic and cultural exchange abroad , and has a good investment environment .
The event focused on equipment manufacturing , logistics and commerce , and the tourism industry . With the sincerity of conspiracy to develop opportunities and work together , it gave a great deal of credit in Urumqi .
