In terms of the world rankings and overall strength of the teams in Group B , the Turkish and Italian teams are the main rivals of the Chinese team .
After the beginning of the match on that day , the Chinese team moved faster into the state of entry , and got ahead at the beginning of the game , maintaining its advantage throughout , putting no less pressure on its opponents on both the balloon and the blocking network , and taking the first step relatively smoothly at 25 : 18 .
The second incoming Turkish team made a fierce bid , starting with a 6 : 2 lead . After the Chinese team requested a pause , it adjusted its battle pattern and gradually scored the score to 7 : 00 , and then repeatedly blocked the Internet to score a score of 7 : 0 . At the end of the scene , the Turkish team scored a score of 15 : 19 . After the Chinese team got the spot at 24 : 20 , the recalcitrant Turkish team scored a score of 2 points . After the Chinese team again requested a pause , the Chinese team scored a score of 25 : 23 for the second scene with Zhu Ting &apos;s running offensive .
The third situation was very colloidal , with the two sides alternating up , and at one point it was 19 @-@ fold flat .
At this critical moment , the Turkish team made a mistake . After leading by 21 : 19 , the Chinese team again relied on Zhu Ting &apos;s strenuous arrest and Zhang Changning &apos;s attack to get a match point of 24 : 21 . Afterwards , the Turkish team scored a score of 23 : 24 . After the Chinese team requested a pause , Zhang Changning scored a score for the attack and the Chinese team scored a victory of 25 : 23 .
Lang Ping , the head coach of the Chinese women &apos;s volleyball team , said frankly after the match that the whole game was not easy .
We are better prepared , we are not bad at blocking the Internet , and the Turkish team is more comprehensive in technology . We must reduce our mistakes and strive to win through our own initiative .
Faced with her familiar teammate in the past , Zhu Ting , who worked for the Wakiofo Bank in Turkey , was subjected to a lot of restrictions in the first part of the match that day , and then she took the initiative to change and still played a strong offensive role .
Both the rival and the rival are very familiar to each other . It is very normal to be watched by the rival . However , the Chinese team has made great use of it . Under the circumstances of the misinformation , both the blocking of the network and the attack have been very good .
Next , the Chinese women &apos;s platoon will hold a truce for one day and conduct physical and technical training ; on October 2 , it will go to the third rival in the team race , the Canadian team .
