The General Administration of Market Supervision recently issued a Circular on Strengthening Market Price Supervision during the National Day in the Mid @-@ Autumn Festival of 2018 , which requires that price regulation in the housing rental and real estate sectors be strengthened , and that price violations such as collusion in rent prices , hoarding of rental housing sources , falsification of false information to inflate rent , disorderly collection of fees through bundling of services , publication of misleading price information , and unspecified prices be severely corrected .
The circular made it clear that early warning of price monitoring should be strengthened and that market price developments should be closely monitored .
Local governments should pay close attention to consumption of food , oil , meat , egg , milk , and other necessities , as well as market and price changes for special commodities consumed by local residents during festivals , and strengthen price monitoring and early warning .
Take timely measures to effectively address market volatility once it is detected that it is tending and emerging .
We should strengthen the supervision and inspection of the wholesale and retail segments of life @-@ necessities , increase the frequency and supervision of places closely related to the daily consumption of the masses such as merchant , agricultural and trade markets , and urge operators to comply with the law and operate in good faith .
The notice pointed out the need to strengthen inspection of key areas and create a good festival consumer environment ; strengthen control of ticket prices in state @-@ owned scenic areas ; focus on investigating and punishing violations in the form of non @-@ implementation of government @-@ mandated price levels or floating margins in state @-@ owned scenic areas , unauthorized addition of fee items , disguised raising of ticket prices , high pricing discounts , tied sales , non @-@ compliance with prescribed code prices , non @-@ implementation of preferential measures , extra @-@ price increases , mandatory surrogate charges , etc .
The notification requires enhanced regulation of prices of essential goods , in particular agricultural products .
Prices of essential agricultural products such as vegetables and pork have fluctuated recently in some areas , affected by seasonal changes , natural disasters and sudden epidemics .
Local governments should take local realities into account , effectively strengthen the regulation of agricultural by @-@ product market prices , work with relevant departments to stabilize production and market supply , and organize forces to carry out market @-@ focused inspections and random spot checks .
For commodities such as pork , where supply is tight and prices are rising faster , more frequent inspections are carried out , and illegal acts such as hoarding strangers , inflating prices and colluding in raising prices are seriously investigated and punished .
The circular indicated that price regulation in the area of housing rental and real estate needed to be strengthened .
In the Mid @-@ Autumn Festival and National Day , which coincide with the boom season in housing rental and commodity housing sales , localities must pay close attention to the price behavior of real estate enterprises , intermediary companies , and housing rental @-@ related enterprises , severely regulate rent price collusion , accumulate sources of rental housing , falsify and fake information to inflate rent , tie @-@ up charges by bundling services , issue misleading price information , and other price violations , increase the level of inspection of the clearly stated prices of hot @-@ selling real estate estates and real estate intermediaries , investigate and deal with non @-@ compliance with regulations that harm consumer interests and disturb market order , clean up the real estate market environment , and create an open and transparent real estate market price order .
The notice referred to the need for localities to effectively regulate prices in other parts of the tourism industry , work hard to standardize the price order in the catering , accommodation , shopping , sightseeing , entertainment , parking , etc . , and guide operators in making clear @-@ cut prices , charging public announcements , and seriously investigate and punish all kinds of price violations .
The notice indicated that the inspection of road , rail , civil aviation , and maritime transport prices should be strengthened , and illegal acts such as price increases , extra @-@ price charges , and non @-@ compliance with the specified code prices should be seriously investigated and punished .
Implement the policy of exempting minibuses from tolls for the transportation of fresh agricultural products through the Green Corridor and on major holidays .
We should innovate regulatory tools and working methods , strengthen the dissemination of price laws and regulations for offline commodity retailers and e @-@ commerce platforms , and urge operators to improve price promotion schemes , and investigate and punish illegal practices such as fictitious original prices , misleading price labelling and non @-@ compliance with price commitments in accordance with the law .
