The station has also set up working exchanges and other mechanisms with the inspection unit , conducted regular counter @-@ terrorism branch exercises at railway ports and joint preventive actions , and constructed a three @-@ tier protection belt for the urban river at the railway ports .
According to reports , in the past 15 years , the border inspection department of the Shanghai Railway has continuously innovated its services , and the speed of customs clearance has greatly increased .
