The fifth World Internet Congress will be held in the town of Wu , Zhejiang , from 7 to 9 November , and the world Internet is about to re @-@ enter the town of Laumu .
As a global Internet event , the World Internet Congress received a high level of attention and widespread recognition in the global Internet arena .
Over the past five years , the World Internet Congress has created a major platform for the exchange of technology on the Internet &apos;s front lines , where the widespread application of technological achievements has given new impetus to global economic development .
Outcome release brings together the world &apos;s Internet frontier technologies
In the field of the Internet , what are the world &apos;s most cutting @-@ edge and visible outcomes ?
The leading scientific and technological results released by the World Internet Congress offer an answer .
For the first time , the Third World Internet Congress released 15 leading scientific and technological outcomes .
The results presented are dynamic , wide @-@ ranging and radiation @-@ led , reflecting the latest and most important breakthroughs in global Internet science and technology at the time , as well as the pace of development and future prospects in the field of cyberinformation .
Photovoltaic computers , 5G , artificial intelligence capable of calculating emotions , etc . The results released at the Fourth World Internet Congress are even more cynical .
The Organizing Committee of the General Assembly set up the World Internet Leading Scientific and Technological Outcomes Recommendation Committee , composed of 44 eminent experts and scholars from 10 countries , including China , the United States and others . It collected nearly 1,000 innovative results in the field of the Internet from countries around the world and finally evaluated 18 representative results , including the three GPP 5G pre @-@ commercial system , the Tornado Arm Security Architecture , the Microsoft Little Ice Baidu satellite navigation system , the Tornado satellite navigation system , based on the light of Dumi Tai Lake ; and the major application results of the supercomputer system , among others .
Currently , the application of the BeiDou satellite navigation system covers more than 50 countries and territories and involves more than 3 billion people .
A total of more than 2 million operational tasks have been carried out on the light of the Shinawatra Lake and more than 100 applications have been supported .
Starting from China , Microsoft Xiaobing , pioneered by Microsoft &apos;s Chinese research and development team , has now landed in China , Japan , the United States , India , Indonesia , and other countries , serving as television host , radio host , singer , and many other roles . China &apos;s Internet technology development has frequently snapped up in the world &apos;s technological frontier camp , attracting the world &apos;s surprising attention and becoming a gathering place and a logo for the world &apos;s leading technologies on the Internet .
Building a new platform for technology exchange at the Internet Light Expo
As one of the key elements of the World Internet Congress , the Internet Oscar Fair drives the interactive exchange of global science , technology and innovation outcomes on the Internet , creating an important platform for Internet enterprises to present the latest results .
The Internet Light Fair showcased new Internet outcomes , new technologies , new applications worldwide , with different thematic exhibition areas and functional segments , selected globally renowned Internet enterprises and innovative enterprises according to different scientific classifications , pooled cutting @-@ edge results , showcased innovative technologies , and reflected the civilized light of Internet exchanges , the light of the future and the light of the world .
To take the example of the Fourth World Internet Congress &apos;s Innocenti Expo , which attracted 411 prominent domestic and foreign companies from around the world to the Expo , its products covered the latest results of global Internet technologies such as cloud computing , Internet of Things , artificial intelligence and the development of applied innovation and the digital economy , highlighting the features of global vision , innovation drive and open cooperation .
More than 110 events on the release of new technologies for new products and 10 Internet project cooperation thematic back @-@ to @-@ back sessions organized during the Congress provided a broad platform for global digital economic cooperation .
A paper test paper , scanned through a cell phone or tablet , can immediately identify the content and change it for distribution . Half a meter high unmanned car carries goods and can independently complete rapid delivery . By order of the host voice alone , the smart home can achieve voice shopping , cell phone charging , hawking , music broadcasting , and a centralized display of top @-@ level Internet science and technology results at the Internet Expo has become the wind mark of global science and technology industry and Internet development , creating a new platform for the exchange of state @-@ of @-@ the @-@ art results .
Internet science and technology development for all
The innovative development driven by Internet technology is ultimately the creation of a better future for the peoples of the world and a more equitable , open and inclusive environment for human well @-@ being , economic development and social well @-@ being .
In a large Internet @-@ based country like China , Internet technology has a strong multiplier effect on specific applications .
For example , Beidou , China , provides high @-@ precision , high @-@ reliability positioning , speed @-@ measuring , timing services to users and has a unique short @-@ message communication capability ; the rapid development of artificial intelligence technology has a remodeling function for traditional industries , promoting industry progress , and playing an active role in many areas such as finance , transportation , health , safety , etc . ; and Earth communications technology has helped to effectively solve the problem of access to airplanes and high @-@ speed railways and improve users &apos; experience of Internet access .
According to the forty @-@ second China Internet Development Statistics Report released by the China Internet Information Center , as the largest Internet market in the world , China is promoting social development through the process of digitization .
And the dividends of Internet technology development are far from limited to China , and its results are a powerful driver of Internet development , and even of economic and social development , throughout the world .
For example , China &apos;s cross @-@ border electricity dealers and sharing economy have become increasingly supportive of world economic growth abroad ; China &apos;s cloud computing , big data , Internet of Things , mobile Internet , and other new generations of information technologies have accelerated the deepening of the global industrial division and economic restructuring , reshaping the competitive pattern of the global economy .
As outlined in the Uu Township Initiative launched at the Second World Internet Congress , sharing the results of network development and promoting the early formation of a global online market to create more jobs will provide a strong basis for sustained and healthy global economic development and allow more countries and people to take the fast trajectory of the information age .
