On the eve of the National Day , during the autumn harvest season , Lu Liang City , which has long been known as the Kingdom of Miao Foodstuff , held a festival of Miao Foodstuff , at which more than 200 businessmen participated in exhibitions with 426 unique and functional foods .
Lu Liang &apos;s potato production is at the forefront of Shanxi . As one of the main production areas , Lang County has in recent years brought villagers out of poverty while developing their industry through the development of potato practices and the extension of the industrial chain . On the spot , exhibitors introduced the new potato eating method through the display of the potato dinner . Businessmen from Lin County brought fresh dates , green beans , peas , millet , etc .
Lu Liang has a long history of agriculture . Grain cultivation began in the New Stone Age . The soybeans , soybeans , barley , piles and others have four or five thousand years of cultivation , with date cultivation going back to West Han .
The unique climate and diverse topography form a large number of unique agricultural products of Lu Liang . They are well @-@ known nationwide production bases for dates , walnuts , petty grains and rosin @-@ type white liquor .
