He sighed with the reporter : It &apos; s really too convenient to use the high - speed railway , and it &apos; s too soon !
Daily shuttle trains to and from southern Guangzhou , northern Shenzhen , and Futian and Xi Jiulong in 70 shifts within one hour greatly facilitated the arrival of residents of Cantonese Hong Kong and Macau in Hong Kong .
