Xinjing News ( Reporter Ni Wei ) On September 29 , the Radio and Television Administration issued a Circular on Launching Special Management Work on Radio and Television Advertising , starting immediately until the end of the year .
The content includes advertisements on low @-@ quality content , tone and low @-@ grade issues , and unrecorded broadcast programmes on medical sustenance .
According to the notice , the focus of the special remediation work this time was on finding and restructuring around nine areas .
These include : advertisements with problems of orientation ; advertisements with problems of low content , tone and grade ; advertisements with excessive and irregular broadcasting ; advertisements with problems of exaggerating false propaganda , misleading audiences , or disguised distribution in the form of programmes ; advertisements with problems of medical care , medicines , medical equipment , health food , cosmetics , cosmetics , cosmetics , etc . ; unrecorded and unauthorized broadcasting of problematic medical breeding programmes ; advertisements with expectations of return on investment that exaggerate false advertising , mislead audiences , lure the audience into becoming deceived ; advertisements with problems of inducing minors to behave improperly or to develop bad values to the detriment of the mental and physical health of minors ; advertisements with problems of prolonged and frequent broadcasting of public service advertisements that fail to meet the requirements ; advertisements with inadequate advertising management systems , inadequate censorship and inadequate accountability ; advertisements with other
This remediation will be fully covered throughout the country , and the requirements of the remediation and regulation will be fully implemented to all levels of the radio and television media , frequency of channels , programmes and time slots , leaving no blind areas , no dead corners , and no exceptions .
The notice requires that all types of illegal advertisements discovered in the supervisory inspection be handled by the Radio and Television Administration at all levels in strict compliance with the General Administration &apos;s &quot; Measures for Handling Irregularities in Radio and Television Broadcasting Agencies . &quot;
If the violations are serious , they should be seriously dealt with , such as admonition , notification of criticism , suspension of advertisement broadcasts until frequency channel broadcasts are suspended , and publicly exposed to the public as appropriate .
In recent years , the General Directorate of Radio and Television has repeatedly suspended illegal advertisements .
This year , the State Radio and Television Administration issued a notice publicly calling off advertisements containing serious irregularities such as deviations and exaggerating exaggerated propaganda and misleading audiences .
The General Directorate of Radio and Television has prepared a number of regulations and circulars regulating the broadcasting of radio and television advertisements .
The Circular on Further Strengthening the Administration of Television Shopping Short Television Advertising stipulates that TV Shopping Short Television Advertising shall not be broadcast between 1800 and 2400 hours per day .
When television shopping short film advertisements are broadcast at other times , they may not use the host to publicize them , they may not use the banquet @-@ selling style to promote them , they may not use the banquet , the banquet , the banquet , the banquet , the banquet , the banquet , the banquet , or other propaganda or disguised propaganda to promote rich chest and reduced weight products , and they may not broadcast television shopping short film advertisements every hour for more than one ( second ) article for no more than three minutes each .
The Circular on Further Strengthening the Regulation of Broadcasting of Radio and Television Advertisements stipulates that television stations must strictly abide by the provisions of the General Directorate &apos;s Order No. 61 when inserting advertisements in movies : 2 commercial advertisements per episode of non @-@ golden time ( in 45 minutes ) , not exceeding 1 minute and 30 seconds per episode ; 1 commercial advertisement per episode of golden time ( 19 : 00 to 21 : 00 ) , not exceeding 1 minute ; and when inserting advertisements , the duration of advertisement should be indicated .
The circular also stipulates that radio and television broadcasters shall strictly examine the qualifications and certification of health information advertisements , such as medical treatment , medicines , medical equipment and health food , and strictly prohibit the broadcasting of sexual advertisements .
To regulate the forms of advertising of health information , advertisements may not be disguised in the form of special programmes on health information .
Health information programmes should focus on scientific knowledge , such as disease prevention , control and treatment , and should not contain advertisements for medical treatment , medicines , medical devices , health food , etc . , or be certified in the name of patients and doctors , pharmacists , experts , etc .
