e said that China will urgently study and propose a phased construction of a free @-@ trade port policy and institutional system in Hainan , and accelerate the process of exploring the construction of a Chinese @-@ specific free @-@ trade port ; a new section of the Shanghai free @-@ trade zone will be added ; a science board will be set up at the Shanghai Securities Exchange and a pilot registration system will be set up to support regional integration and development in the Yangtze Delta region and will be upgraded to a national strategy .
The Chinese economy is a sea , not a small pond .
