China will stimulate import potential , adjust to the upward trend in domestic consumption , and take more proactive and effective measures to boost household income and nurture middle- and high @-@ end consumption growth points .
China will respect international business practices and treat all types of enterprises registered in China equally and equally .
China will protect the legitimate rights and interests of foreign @-@ owned enterprises , resolutely punish infringements of the legitimate rights and interests of foreign investors , in particular infringements of intellectual property rights , improve the quality of intellectual property censorship and efficiency of censorship , and introduce a punitive compensation system , significantly raising the costs of infringements .
