Ni Youfeng , Chief Engineer of the Visible Area Management Committee , said to the media that this was the longest extension of the high water level on the Yellow River in nearly 20 years . It was never so long before . Our flood closure period in 2017 was 4 days , and this year it was nearly a month .
ccording to reports , the Yellow River Falls in Shanxi originally increased its staffing arrangements and vehicle maintenance ahead of schedule in anticipation of the eleventh Golden Week , and even hired temporary staff have already been put in place .
