On the evening of the 29th , the reporter learned from the Propaganda Department of Qinghai @-@ Bai Jiang District in Chengdu City that on the evening of September 29th , Beijing time , a series of Central European Banlings ( Chengdu ) full of car connectors , telescopes , liquid crystal display screens and other goods were replaced and switched to Nürnberg , Germany , via the Polish port of Semia Nufka .
This was the first time in Central Europe that Banlje opened the Polish port of Semia Nufka , marking the successful opening of another European transport route in Central Europe after Marra and Jupp .
This trip to Central Europe began on September 14 at the Qinghai @-@ Bai railway station in Chengdu , exited through the Alasan mouth , entered Europe through the Schemianufka border crossing in Poland , and eventually reached Nuremberg , Germany , for a total of about 16 days .
For the first time in Central Europe , a shift to a wide @-@ range rail and a trajectory has taken place here .
The opening of the port effectively addressed the current problems of long hours of operation and long periods of time caused by congestion at the port of Mala , increasing the length of scheduled traffic ; it also provided a new solution to the problem of congestion at the port of Mala , further improving the capacity and efficiency of transport from the western hinterland of China to the Euro @-@ Mediterranean market and laying a solid foundation for the opening of the Central European market .
