ccording to Longguang Information Analyst Li Yan , the preferential promotion strategy in the retail sales of gas stations has not changed much . Currently , the preferential margin for major stations such as Sinopec is more than 0.5 @ - @ 0.7 yuan / l , while the preferential margin for private gas stations is more than 0.5 @ - @ 1.2 yuan / l .
