In the early morning of the 1st , the direction of exit from the ports of Luohu , Shenzhen Bay , Wang Gang , Futian and other ports ushered in peak passenger ( car ) flow , with peak passenger flow from 9 a.m. to 11 a.m. at Luohu port and peak passenger ( car ) flow from 6.30 a.m. to 13 noon at Shenzhen Bay .
According to the introduction , in order to cope with the peak flow of incoming and outgoing passengers ( vehicles ) , the Shenzhen General Border Inspection Station , in accordance with the unified deployment of the State Migration Administration , launched the working mode for peak passenger ( car ) flow periods , arranged for overtime police to support the first line of duty , opened sufficient advance inspection channels , guided passengers and vehicles to check in an orderly manner , and ensured that Chinese citizens were not queued for more than 30 minutes to enter and leave the country , while taking into account the efficiency of customs clearance for foreigners ; and strengthened order maintenance in areas with high flow of people to ensure that customs clearance was conducted in an orderly manner .
Shenzhen &apos;s General Border Inspection Station also reminds incoming and outgoing travelers that they should pay attention to the validity of documents and visas and sign notes before leaving the country , make reasonable arrangements for itineraries , avoid peak passenger flow periods as much as possible , and choose the right time and suitable port for travel .
Passengers travelling to Hong Kong on the Guangzhou @-@ Shenzhen high @-@ speed railway must have valid exit and exit documents and visa stamps . The high @-@ speed rail ticket is only a passenger ticket and cannot be used as an exit and entry document . If they cannot leave Hong Kong for reasons such as non @-@ compliance with documentation procedures , they should follow the guidelines of the civilian police on border inspection and wait for the employees of the Hong Kong Railways Company to take the transportation procedures to the Mainland .
Systemic lupus erythematosus is a chronic and intractable disease of cumbersome multi @-@ dirty machines , which were once thought to be incurable .
They cannot be eradicated because their mechanisms are unknown , they are difficult to diagnose and they lack effective treatment methods .
Recently , a joint team of researchers at Tsinghua University College of Life Sciences , Liu Wanli , and Chestnut @-@ occupied countries , director of the Feng and Wet Immunization Center at Beijing University People &apos;s Hospital , found that human immunoglobulins have molecular variants that increase systemic lupus lupus susceptibility and that such variants are involved in the regulation of immunogenic B cells .
In short , both groups confirmed that an abnormal immunologist in humans was an important cause of systemic lupus erythematosus .
ccording to one of the authors of the article , Sun Xiaolin of Peking University Hospital , the Chestnut Occupation Team collected and conducted research on nearly 2,000 large samples of systemic lupus erythematosus patients , and found that patients with immunoglobulin variants produced pathogenic cells and a wide variety of self @-@ antibodies , with a significant increase in the incidence and severity of inflammation such as nephritis , arthritis , plasma and vascular inflammation .
Liu Wanli &apos;s team discovered this immunomolecular variant @-@ activated immune signaling pathway and promoted the pathogenic mechanism of B @-@ cell secretion of a variety of autoantibodies through various methods of study such as immunocyte traces , animal experiments , sequencing , and the like .
The reporter learned that the two teams were strong and united , fully exploiting their respective strengths and achieving a close connection between basic research and clinical application .
The Liu Wanli team is committed to B lymphocyte immunization recognition and immunostimulation studies , while the Chestnut Occupation team has long been engaged in systemic lupus erythematosus clinical studies .
The study was one of the results of years of collaboration between the two teams and the first institutional recognition in academia that immunoglobulin genetic abnormalities will induce systemic lupus erythematosus , providing a solid foundation for further academic research and clinical targeting .
This is not short @-@ term protection , but rather compliance with the law .
The lawyer brought an axe to the court session ?
At first glance , the news was really stimulating , and the pot was blown up in the legal circle .
Quanzhou City Law in Fujian subsequently fined the lawyer involved 500 yuan and advised the Quanzhou City Bar Association in writing to investigate and deal with the matter .
According to a report by the Beijing News , the Quanzhou City Law Association recently issued an official notice stating that the actions of the two lawyers did not involve violations of the law and were not punished in accordance with the law .
According to multiple reports , the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association &apos;s handling was not short @-@ sighted or confrontational , but was endorsed by the Quanzhou Intermediate Council .
An incident that could have provoked tension within the legal community was eventually properly resolved .
The reversal of the matter stemmed from a more complete truth : the axes carried by the lawyers involved were the same as the murderers of the accused , but were not blunted , were merely corroborated by evidence at the evidentiary stage , were not intimidating or had the subjective intention of endangering the safety of the court .
There are four very important details for judging whether the conduct of the lawyer involved was unlawful : first , two previous sessions of the local court , in which only an axe photograph was presented and , from the point of view of the defence , the axe was necessary ; second , the axe was purchased only one hour before the hearing , not because the lawyer did not wish to seek the judge &apos;s consent , but because he did not objectively have access to the judge ; third , the axe was not used excessively or inappropriately ; and fourth , the lawyer in question publicly recognized the error at the first time and apologized to the court .
Taken together these circumstances , it can be seen that the lawyer involved in the matter took the hawkish to appear in court and did nothing to do anything but to defend himself .
After clarifying the whole fact , the Quanzhou City Law Association did not push the boat along , but instead took the decision not to punish under pressure .
This decision also meets the test of fact and law .
As for bringing axes used as control knives into the courtroom without the permission of the court , this is indeed a source of anxiety and misunderstanding .
For reasons of safety and prudence , previous fines and judicial advice from the Quanzhou Intermediate Court are also well founded .
In order to preserve the dignity of lawyers and prevent individual courts from harassing lawyers , the Supreme Law issued the &quot; Rules of the Judicial Police of the People &apos;s Court on Security Censorship &quot; in 2014 , establishing the principle that the presence of a lawyer in court does not require a physical security check .
Since the issuance of the rule , a wide range of lawyers have led by example , with few incidents in which the security of the court has been jeopardized by security gaps .
In very few cases , such as Quanzhou , misunderstanding can easily be overcome by communicating in a spirit of mutual respect and understanding .
As a self @-@ regulatory organization of the legal profession , the Bar Association has the dual mandate of disciplining wrongdoing and safeguarding legality .
In the past , individual law societies have been criticized for their focus on discipline and loss of security .
And the Quanzhou Law Association &apos;s decision , both in terms of process and outcome , is laudable , setting an example for more law societies to perform their duties properly .
From October 1 , which taxes and benefits will affect our money bags ?
Xinhua News Agency , Shanghai , October 1 ( Reporter Song Tong ) - The new personal income tax law will be implemented on January 1 , 2019 . In order for the general public to enjoy the tax relief dividend as soon as possible , from October 1 , the actual salary income earned by taxpayers will be deducted at the starting point of 5,000 yuan per month , and a new tax scale will be applied .
With the arrival of the New Deal , what good interests will affect the money bags of the masses ?
Good 1 : Remarkable tax reduction on wages and salaries
Taxpayers who receive wages after October 1 can deduct a basic deduction of 5,000 yuan per month and apply a new tax scale , with most taxpayers having different levels of tax cuts , particularly for low- and middle @-@ income people .
According to the tax relief table for the different income groups , the monthly income after deduction of the sum of $ 8,000 , $ 10,000 , $ 20,000 and $ 50,000 , respectively , after tax reform is $ 90 , $ 290 , $ 1590 and $ 9090 . Compared to the monthly threshold of $ 3,500 , the corresponding tax deductions are 73.9 per cent , 61.1 per cent , 49.0 per cent and 18.8 per cent , respectively .
It is worth noting that , for holiday reasons , new base deductions and tax schedules may be applied to the wages paid by the units in accordance with the law at the end of September , which were due in October .
To this end , the customized withholding client software used by tax administrations already provides the corresponding tax calculation function , but the corresponding tax remains to be reported during the statutory filing period .
Good two : a significant increase in the low @-@ tax range
In addition to raising the threshold , a new scale will be applied effective 1 October .
This time , the seven @-@ step tax rate on wages and salaries is the same as before , but there has been a marked change in the tax range , with a significant increase in the three @-@ tier low @-@ tax range of 3 per cent , 10 per cent and 20 per cent , a decrease in the 25 per cent tax range and the 30 per cent , 35 per cent and 45 per cent higher tax range remaining unchanged .
It is worth noting that the tax law also adjusted the tax rates for each tranche of production income , with the lower limit of the top 35 per cent rate being raised from 100,000 yuan to 500,000 yuan .
This means that individual business owners and individual sole @-@ source partnerships will all benefit from tax reform .
Looking at the earlier estimates of personal tax cuts for Shanghai taxpayers , the dividends of tax reform will be fully felt by the majority of taxpayers , especially among low- and middle @-@ income people .
Lanmin , head of the personal income tax department of the Shanghai Municipal Tax Administration of the State Administration of Taxation , said .
Good Three : Ease and Optimization of Tax Services
Since the publication of the new personal income tax law , the Shanghai tax authorities have carried out a wide range of wide @-@ ranging tax campaigns .
On the one hand , they carry out one @-@ on @-@ one , one @-@ on @-@ one , one @-@ on @-@ one policy coaching for key tax sources and key enterprises .
The Pudong New District Taxation Bureau visited Apple Trading ( Shanghai ) Ltd . , Fabao ( China ) Network Technology Ltd . , Red Star Meiceron Home Group Co . , Ltd . , and other large enterprises . These enterprises have a large number of employees , a large volume of tax deductions , a large amount of tax payments , and the tax department &apos;s initiative to mentor and answer questions . The Xuxi Huxi District Taxation Bureau visited the large labor enterprises in the region , Zhongqi Financial Consulting Ltd . , and the China @-@ Chile Shanghai Economic and Technical Cooperation Corporation , among others , to collect business concerns in a timely manner , respond to business demands and resolve business difficulties .
On the other hand , a comprehensive , multi @-@ dimensional , and integrated tax policy is being implemented for all citizens and taxpayers .
Use the official Shanghai tax website , WeChat public number , Weibo and other channels to push policy hot spots in a timely manner to ensure that policy advocacy is in place .
At the same time , since September 28 , the Shanghai Tax WeChat public address on the 12366 intelligent consultation platform , through the manual + intelligent consultation on tax services , has launched a tax reform advocacy service on targeted forms of intelligent integration .
