According to foreign media reports , a joint statement by Canadian Foreign Minister Frillan and US Trade Representative Letsizer , published on the Canadian government website , said that the United States , Canada and Mexico had entered into a trilateral trade agreement that would be known as the USMCA &apos; s ( US @-@ Mexico trilateral agreement ) .
Earlier , Canada &apos;s CTV News quoted high @-@ level sources in the United States as saying that Canada and the United States had resolved their differences and reached an agreement on the North American Free Trade Agreement ( NAFTA ) .
he Washington Post quoted two informed sources as reporting that the September 30 agreement between the United States and Canada would keep NAFTA as a tripartite trade agreement , and that the three heads of state would sign the new agreement within two months .
